      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I know I should talk to them. But looking at these new guidelines they sent over, it seems like a huge downgrade. They want to strip out basically all the grit and complexity we've been working on. I'm honestly not sure if the book will even be worth publishing if it's this watered down. What do you think happens to our workflow if I just... don't let them apply the update right away?",
